Package: InduTrace
Title: Industrial Tracer for contaminants from time-series
Version: 0.0.0.1000
Authors@R: 
    person("Teofana", "Chonova", , "teofana.chonova@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: InduTrace (Industrial Tracer) is designed to help users prioritize 
               and classify contaminants based on their temporal patterns and identify contaminants with 
               similar patterns in time-profiles from long-term, high-frequency river monitoring data. 
